{"id":124977,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/简讯：北京拟派官员到美国挂职/","date":"2010-11-23T13:24:16Z","modified":"2010-11-23T13:24:16Z","title":"简讯：北京拟派官员到美国挂职","content":"<div>\n<p>北京东城区提出，未来打算派官员到美国挂职工作。</p>\n<p>该区希望派官员到美国城市的科技、城市建设、规划和管理部门工作。</p>\n<p>北京媒体引官员说，到国外挂职工作的效果要优于到国外大学进修。</p>\n<p>东城区称，近几年该区都选送官员到韩国或香港挂职。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/bLbl3rE_3xe_JV7dpSaytCLMgWs/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/bLbl3rE_3xe_JV7dpSaytCLMgWs/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/bLbl3rE_3xe_JV7dpSaytCLMgWs/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/bLbl3rE_3xe_JV7dpSaytCLMgWs/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=9XAsXYTN7gM:oLbilBkF2vE:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=9XAsXYTN7gM:oLbilBkF2vE:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=9XAsXYTN7gM:oLbilBkF2vE:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=9XAsXYTN7gM:oLbilBkF2vE:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=9XAsXYTN7gM:oLbilBkF2vE:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=9XAsXYTN7gM:oLbilBkF2vE:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/9XAsXYTN7gM\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2010/11/1